title: IAA Tonight | Are the Eagles the Best Team in the NFL?
description: Baltimore Ravens CB Marcus Peters was visibly frustrated and seen yelling towards coach John Harbaugh on the sideline for another late game collapse. Why can't the Ravens close out games with big leads? Plus, are the Philadelphia Eagles the best team in the NFL as they remain undefeated on the season at 4-0?
author: smanderville@houseofathlete.com (Leger Douzable, Omar Kelly, Adam pacman jones)
